text: Meherzia Labidi Ma誰za (;17 December 1963 - 21/22 January 2021) was a Tunisian politician and professional translator. She was a member of the Assembly of the Representatives of the People from 2011 to 2019 and from 2020 until her death. She was a member of the Ennahda Movement. Labidi Ma誰za was born in Hammamet, Tunisia. Labidi Ma誰za died of COVID-19 in Paris, France in January 2021, aged 57. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Paris Category:Translators Category:Tunisian politicians
